Package checker

Class Checker

java.lang.Object
grammar.PickleCannonBaseListener
checker.Checker
All Implemented Interfaces:
PickleCannonListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class Checker
extends PickleCannonBaseListener
Checker class is a class that is responsible for the elaboration phase of compiler. Class extends PickleCannonBaseListener and by overriding listener methods performs the elaboration. The result of elaboration is the object of Result class.
Author:
Karolis Butkus
